Class GVRWorld

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gearvrf.GVRHybridObject
      • org.gearvrf.GVRComponent
        • org.gearvrf.GVRBehavior
          • org.gearvrf.physics.GVRWorld
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.gearvrf.GVRDrawFrameListener, org.gearvrf.GVRSceneObject.ComponentVisitor, org.gearvrf.IEvents, org.gearvrf.ILifeCycleEvents, org.gearvrf.ISceneObjectEvents

    public class GVRWorld
extends org.gearvrf.GVRBehavior
implements org.gearvrf.ISceneObjectEvents, org.gearvrf.GVRSceneObject.ComponentVisitor
    Represents a physics world where all GVRSceneObject with GVRRigidBody component attached to are simulated.

    GVRWorld is a component that must be attached to the scene's root object.
